#: src/msmtp.c:2294
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Sendmail mode (default):\n"
"  %s [option...] [--] recipient...\n"
"  %s [option...] -t [--] [recipient...]\n"
"  Read a mail from standard input and transmit it to an SMTP or LMTP server.\n"
